Final Match
According to the tournament regulations, the final match would have to be played
in Belo Horizonte, however Vasco da Gama complained of security problems in the
Minerão stadium and CBD decided to transfer the match to Rio de Janeiro.
  
[Aug 1]
Vasco da Gama   2-1  Cruzeiro
  
Final match details
Venue: Maracanã (Rio de Janeiro).
Attendance: 112.933
Referee: Armando Marques (SP)
Goals:
1-0 Ademir 14'                         1-1 Nelinho 19'
2-1 Jorginho Carvoeiro 78'
